        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Family demand, generous blocks</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/stafford" style="color:#b98229;">Stafford</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kedron" style="color:#b98229;">Kedron</a>, <a href="/suburbs/wavell-heights" style="color:#b98229;">Wavell Heights</a>.</p>
